  <name>Linux Task Manager</name>
  <summary>Monitor and manage system processes</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Linux Task Manager allows you to monitor system processes, CPU usage, memory usage, 
      network activity, and disk I/O in real-time. It provides an intuitive interface to 
      view and manage running processes on your Linux system.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Real-time process monitoring</li>
      <li>CPU, memory, network, and disk usage graphs</li>
      <li>Process management (end processes)</li>
      <li>Customizable refresh rates</li>
      <li>Dark mode support</li>
      <li>Responsive UI design</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
